## ♂️ Male Reproductive Organs

| Structure | Function |
|-----------|----------|
| [[Testes]] | Spermatogenesis + testosterone production |
| [[Epididymis]] | Sperm maturation and storage |
| [[Vas Deferens]] | Sperm transport from epididymis to ejaculatory duct |
| [[Seminal Vesicles]] | Secrete fructose-rich fluid (~70% of semen volume) |
| [[Prostate Gland]] | Secretes alkaline fluid; contains PSA |
| [[Bulbourethral Glands]] | Pre-ejaculatory lubrication (Cowper's glands) |
| [[Spermatic Cord]] | Carries vas deferens, testicular artery, pampiniform plexus |
| [[Scrotum]] | Thermoregulatory housing for testes |
| [[Penis]] | Erectile organ; urinary + reproductive conduit |

